<br>
    With all prudence the rogues slip into shadows and the casters with the magic to do so cast and make themselves and the others invisible, so that they can wait together unseen to deal with the intruder if it gains entry. Suddenly the glow of discharged mana  shines from under the door just as it bursts inward from an even greater blow. An ogre stumbles through the wreckage then looks around.<br>
    “Oops, sorry. Me cleans up mess.&quot; He steps forward. “ Hullo? Me know you in here. Me can feel your lookers looking. Me Stryven. Me need your help. You tell Stryven where me can find Hebben?&quot;<br>
<br>
    He looks around in the silence then speaks. “Me come from Steemfont. Me happy gnome boy till bad day happen. Mommy say “Be good boy, go play, mommy real tired.” Mommy tired a lot. Me wants to be good boy so me go play with cowheads till they break. Then me go home, but Mommy gone. Me ask Daddy “Where Mommy?” He say “Angels come and take Mommy to Hebben.” Me say “ When she come back?” Then Daddy’s face rain and he say “She can’t come back.” Then he go in house. Me can’t fit in house so me sits outside and thinks. Me not good thinker but me tries real hard.  Me think bad angels take Mommy and won’t let her come home. Me decides me go find bad angels and tell them to give Mommy back! If angels say no, me bonk angels till they say yes.”<br>
<br>
    Stryven waits for a reply, receiving none he continues. “ Me touch big book that takes you places and me go to nice place called ‘Planes of Brains’ or sumthin like that. Me meet funny lookin  shaman guy. He show Stryven how to throw magic stuffs. Then he say ‘Go away’, me go.”<br>
<br>
    “Mommy say ‘Be good Coodles.’ You no call me Coodles, Me bash you! Only Mommy call me special love name. Maybe me let Sumwun Special call me that too. Me not meet her yet but Mommy says me will know her cause she’ll make me feel special happy like Mommy.”<br>
<br>
    “Sorry, me get stracted . Me want to be good for Mommy but how can me be good if Mommy not here to tell Stryven what good is? So me need help finding Mommy. Me promise to help you, bestest I can. Me good lifter. Me lift many heavy things, me even lift things for Daddy and him big strong paladin guy. And me good at breaking things too. And me bash anything you want. You help me find Mommy?”<br>
<br>
    After a long pause He stands a little straighter and knits his brow. “Okey dokey, Me understands. Maybe you no talk to poor gnome guys looking for Mommies. Maybe you like the other guild places, you no talk to people with just only little names. Maybe me come back later when me have big name like ‘Stryven BiggnomewhofindshisMommy. Maybe not. Me go now. Bye-Bye.”<br>
<br>
    With that he heads back to the entrance. Stopping amid the wreckage of the door he says just loud enough to hear, “You no help Stryven, me no pick up mess, Hee hee!”<br>
<br>
    Stepping into the alleyway he grabs a passing dwarf by the neck, &quot;Hey dwarfy guy, you help gnome find Hebben? No no, don’t wiggle! Me no hurt you, no wiggle. STOP! Oops.”<br>
    Looking around He sees a Priestess of Marr, “Hey Priest Lady, You fix dwarf? Him help gnome but him broke. No no, don’t run. Okay me play Catchme game with you. Ready or not here I come……. <br>
<br>
